{
  "texts": [
    "In addition, a novel loss function tailored to the ISAC network was developed.",
    "Compared to the model-based transceiver, their scheme achieved comparable performance with higher robustness to hardware impairments.",
    "Following a similar scenario, Mateos-Ramos et al. [236] proposed a model-driven E2E learning for ISAC systems, demonstrating better generalization than the data-driven E2E counterpart.",
    "Specifically, domain knowledge was used to guide the design of neural networks at the ISAC transceiver.",
    "Zheng et al. [237] proposed an E2E learning approach for symbol-level precoding-based ISAC networks."
  ]
}